{"tid":344180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"按摩棒狂打男生臀致瘀黑　女補習教師判服務令","createTime":"2017-08-02T05:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T14:46:13.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1000c6d322d20fe6e68b7f2fb846625035a13ca9","tid":344180,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"投身教育工作18年的女補習教師，面對11歲男生反覆答錯同一條數學題，突然發怒執起膠製按摩棒狂打男生臀部20次致瘀黑，被捕後更聲稱是為男生好。案件今判刑，心理醫生報告透露被告認為應嚴格對待男生，又認為體罰合理，但辯方律師稱被告只是引述其他人看法，被告的意思是指「佢自己唔會」。裁判官接納求情，最終判被告接受100小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n被告胡翠琼（48歲）承認一項故意襲擊致兒童受損害罪，早前被裁判官還柙兩星期，辯方今在庭上指，被告家人及前學生得悉被告還柙及有機會判監感到震驚和擔心，先後為被告撰寫共22封求情信。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官判刑時指，案情嚴重之處是違反誠信，家長將小孩交給被告，卻遭暴力對待，而事主的傷勢範圍頗大，惟被告已還柙2星期，相信已汲取教訓。"},{"pid":"3d8a0f0e965cbdf3fa578a82ecb8a7cc6b939db9","tid":344180,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170802&amp;guid=57031208&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170802%26guid%3D57031208%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml49tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=46a0f6ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170802%26guid%3D57031208%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=8cc82407\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170802&amp;guid=57031208&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"ff3af8be5a525c9a4228e1f1534d7ee49c5e0d9c","tid":344180,"uid":1082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"膠製按摩棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 姐係。。。。。"},{"pid":"dfe2352d33a0a3ccfd54342dea615178fcfd5d6e